title: From Humble Beginnings (Joe Steel) - Harwood, Ian.epub
description:
This is only part one, it is more than just a coming of age story.
It deals with a love triangle, corporate backbiting, the difficulties in trying to retain a chunk of the huge global market as well as the interference from locals. From the mafia to insurance fraud, Joe sees it all in his attempt to reach and then to stay at the top of his game.
Genre: Romance
